Usage: _build/macosx64/bin/infinit-device MODE [OPTIONS...]			Usage: infinit-device device [MODE|--help]
										Infinit device management utility.
Infinit device utility:
										Modes:
Modes:										  receive    Receive an object from another device using https://beyond.infinit
  --transmit		       Transmit object to another device using the Hub	  transmit   transmit an object to another device using https://beyond.infinit.
  --receive		       Receive an object from another device using the
			       Hub						Options:
										  -h, --help		    show this help message
Miscellaneous:
  -h [ --help ]		       Display the help
  -s [ --script ]	       Silence all extraneous human friendly messages
  --compatibility-version arg  Force compatibility version
  -v [ --version ]	       Display version
  --critical-log	       Path to critical log file, none to disable
  -a [ --as ] arg	       User to run commands as (default: system user)
